{"tid":1956224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：市民儲起派錢計劃收款削弱帶動消費的初衷","createTime":"2020-04-03T04:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T11:54:15.000Z","uid":21470,"like":11,"dislike":161,"uniUserReply":126,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f80a5fe8fc969f2ada9f01d7df9981f3fafae1","tid":1956224,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T04:58:29.000Z","msg":"立法會研究：派錢計劃可再分配收入惟仍有不足<br />\n03.04.2020 12:26<br />\n立法會秘書處就財政預算案發表研究報告，指1200億元的紓緩措施中，有六成三是發放現金和支援低收入家庭，相較過去五份預算案，有較明顯的收入再分配效應，但認為過往要19個月才完成派錢，較澳門及新加坡的4至10個月為長，行政費亦達10億元，似乎過高，部份收款人可能會儲起現金，尤其是富裕人士，變相削弱帶動本地消費的效果。<br />\n<br />\n研究又指，人口老化將加重社會服務需求，勞動人口減少，加上稅基狹窄，不能排除長遠會出現結構性赤字的風險。研究又認為，香港經歷去年的社會風波，如果未能消除海外機構對本港的疑慮，長遠可能影響稅基。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278511&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278511%26csid%3D261_341&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=0031f8d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278511&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"d6cecaeec968d9ee8f2762d90bea186972ce18f9","tid":1956224,"uid":73269,"like":245,"dislike":0,"score":245,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T04:59:56.000Z","msg":"人地點洗關你然事"},{"pid":"10e923aa517aa1cd72ab58263ab8360ff20ef933","tid":1956224,"uid":62755,"like":230,"dislike":4,"score":226,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"儲錢又關你事<br />\n即係派錢係為商家，唔係為民生"},{"pid":"05c71d83dac654461bbe3e30e76d533bc35d449b","tid":1956224,"uid":284855,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:01:00.000Z","msg":"轉埋美金先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bde4f54967d4edde1867b24ce0ccceb4b138fd0","tid":1956224,"uid":247184,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:01:30.000Z","msg":"派俾死黑警就唔駛分配"},{"pid":"76aa65ef19a843172319c8d55df11d939dbf700e","tid":1956224,"u